     1ÔćĺThis directory contains "newsfragments" which are short files that contain a small **ReST**-formatted
     2Ôćĺtext that will be added to the next ``CHANGELOG``.
     3Ôćĺ
     4ÔćĺThe ``CHANGELOG`` will be read by users, so this description should be aimed to pytest users
